==Japanese==

===Conjunction===
'''なぜなら''' (názenara)

# "that is because"
#* なぜなら appears at the beginning of a sentence. It is almost always paired with the phrase [[からだ]] at the end of the sentence.
#* なぜなら[[古い]]からだ。 (názenara furúi kará da) &mdash; That is because [it] is old.

See also: [[なぜ]], [[なら]]

